Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.6\shad2\4a&HFF&}Okay, three, two, one let's jam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. So how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nothing to do with the syndicate...\N- He was just a regular employee...\N- They were just thugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- just dead-end kids who wanted money...\N- who gave into temptation...\N- that got their stash stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- They're all on their way to juvie.\N- The poor sap's behind bars.\N- They went to the cops stone broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught every criminal\Non the whole list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't pick up any\Nleads or clues? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still using paper to\Nsend in their complaints...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just harassment.\NWaste of resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And our server's gone down\Nfrom all the e-complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's a movement out there\Nto sue the company for damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the damn bounty\Nhunters when you need them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We put out a huge\Nbounty on the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,True, but maybe it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi, amigos! All you bad\Nbounty hunters, how y'all doin'?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, it's time for Big Shot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's today's hot news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They caught the lowdown outlaws who\Ncarried out those recent gate attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really? The bounty on that guy\Nwas 12 million Woolongs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said outlaws.\NThey caught twenty of 'em.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What do you mean, Punch?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like they were caught in the act,\Nbut none of them was the mastermind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, well, you don't get the reward\Nunless you find the mastermind, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shucks howdy, that's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then the guys who caught 'em\Ndon't get a penny. Sorry, you guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the kind of two-bit hoods\Nwho usually rob convenience stores
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly attack an astral gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Maybe it's\Na new fad for criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... "Hey, kids, if you're a fashion-\Nconscious young hood, remember,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"that cute girl won't even look your way\Nunless you knock over an astral gate."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Do it today!"\NYou mean like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all pony up the\Ninformation we have on this case
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and agree to split the bounty\Nthree ways? What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right? You're the one\Nwho said to work separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Each one gathering the facts\Nand examining them..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Occasional rivalry between\Ncomrades is healthy."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's the way you put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the size of the reward\Nscramble your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You guys are\Nreally keen on the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we each wanted the bounty\Nto put in our own pockets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All twenty hits were\Ndone the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of them\Ninfiltrated the tollbooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And attached the hacking\Nunit very precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So when a ship was coming through,\Nat the exact moment it paid the toll,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they could steal the entire\Nbalance from the credit chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The unit immediately sent the cash credits\Nover a secured link to a bank on Europa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There, the money was electronically\Nlaundered through a series
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of blind transactions that\Ncan't be traced in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All the culprits were caught in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them have anything in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Age, gender, nationality,\Nreligion, criminal record... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, not one of them\Nhad a single stolen Woolong on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's all the information\NI could get. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I nabbed was so clueless,\Nhe said he was following the instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from a manual he got\Nmail-order from some website.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the other thieves were all wannabes\Nwho read the same manual, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"All new criminal support software."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Act now for this special offer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"For the low introductory\Nprice of 30,000 Woolongs,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"you can be a billionaire."\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complicated to be\Nan outlaw nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So some people use\Nmanuals to help them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this mail-order company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In cyberspace. It's virtual.\NThere's no actual location.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the website's\Ngone without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Those hacking units weren't\Ndesigned by some piker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an insider who knows\Nprecisely how the gate system works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's behind it is probably\Nconnected to the gate corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my take on it.\NI tried to look into it, but uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- You mean a crooked programmer?\N- Right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But the guys from the gate corporation\Nsuddenly became very uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if they\Nknew it was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but they didn't wanna\Ntalk about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, wait a minute... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These pieces are it.\NThey're still our best clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a memory cartridge\Nfor playing e-chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory chip stores\Ndata within the piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can activate one game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It connects to the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this has something to do\Nwith the incidents at the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this whole thing with the\Nastral gate is really just a big game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and play against\Nyour cyber opponent, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try dealing with the\Ngate corporation again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,1-2-3-4,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed's gonna score more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Another bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what he wants.\NSend him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he looking for a programmer\Nwho likes to play chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, eh, Jon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You went through all that trouble\Nfor nothing, like an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is much tougher\Nthan it looks, Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You read our bounty bulletin.\NAll the information is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very straightforward.\NWhat else do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid there's no smoking\Nallowed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't have\Nany questions. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's something I want you to see.\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a game.\NAll planned out in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You gate guys know exactly\Nwhat I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You put a bounty out on some\Nmastermind who may not even exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which means you don't want the police\Nto know who's really behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You suits are using us\Nbounty hunters like pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bounty hunters should look for bounties.\NI suggest you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you used to work\Nfor the ISSP, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you'd be wise\Nto drop this line of inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guest is leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure he's escorted\Nout of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We should've never taken such a risk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If this thing ever gets out,\Nyou know what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware of the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if we don't catch him fast,\Nthe situation can only get worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why would a ghost from fifty\Nyears ago suddenly come back now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't make any sense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he gives everyone\Na chess piece... unbelievable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Chessmaster Hex...{\i0}\N- {\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The whole thing really\Nis a game for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chessmaster Hex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. There's nothing\Nin here but chess data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they were planning\Nto do with these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the data doesn't\Nhave any meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but what if the chess pieces themselves\Nare some kinda message?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Spike, I've got an ID.\NSee what you can find on him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He could be the so-called\Nmastermind behind this thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward is very busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Check-check-check-checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... so Ed thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least my knight\Ntakes your rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky, this is either\Nan idiot or a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chessmaster Hex.\NEstimated to be 98 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A programmer that had been\Ndubbed a genius from his teens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Cosmonet chess tournaments,\Nhe held the champion's seat for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He applied his intellect to\Nthe Hyperspace Gate Project,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,joining the program at 30 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He eventually developed the central control\Nsystem that all gates use to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But after that,\Nhe started to have doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the design had defects,\Nand the gates shouldn't be built yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to run more tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So they fired him and\Nbuilt the gates anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been missing for\Nthe last fifty years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's the mastermind\Nwho taught those beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Is he trying to get revenge\Nafter all these years, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we track him down,\Nwe can get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Ed.\N- Edward is very busy. Try later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget later, we need some help, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme that--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed, we're trying to find a guy\Nnamed Hex. He's in cyberspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hex, Hex, the Chessmaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward is playing chess\Nagainst him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tracked him through Edward's game,\Nand we're coming up on him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys standing by?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this. He made it\Nmuch too easy to trace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's too smart for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a false trail.\NI mean, look where we're heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Would he be in a dump like that?\N- Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard about this place a long time ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A kind of floating scrapyard where\Nthey leave wrecked gate parts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}abandoned spaceships, and scrap metal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People moved in and started living there.\NSquatters and drifters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why the hell would they\Nwanna live there of all places?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no government, no nationality,\Nno taxes, and no cops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They see it as total freedom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, right... It'd also make it\Na perfect place to hide out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remember, this could be a trap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A continuation of the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's air in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then there's someone there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How's it going, Jet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jonathan! What are you doing out here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tracking you, of course.\NThanks for leading the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you've been\Nfollowing us? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like this. I've got a score to\Nsettle with the guy you're looking for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye-bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace to the whole galaxy.\NAnd to my bank account, love love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chessmaster Hex, I take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try anything, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You both...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, could you be just\Na little quieter, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretending to be senile\Nwon't get you outta this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who are you?\N- Either you give me the money you took,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,or I put a hole right through your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a large pipe there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whatcha doin', Hex?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My first formidable opponent in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be some player to pin you down.\NWhat's your next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...\NLet's have lunch first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate lunch a few\Nminutes ago, blast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Did I like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know. But {\i1}this{\i0} one is losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave your brain somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like {\i1}you{\i0} can talk, you numbskull.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My life savings gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get it back now,\Ndammit... goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone and everyone\Nin the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do with him?\NThe old duffer's out of touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't recall yesterday,\Nlet alone fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky for him, Hex is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one left but an old man\Nwho loves to play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hex was furious. He wanted revenge,\Nand this is how he got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He set up the sting\Nto kick in fifty years later
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when the gate was prescheduled\Nfor its first automatic tech upgrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all planned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He even arranged for his\Noperatives to carry chess pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to let you know that he had\Nfinally gotten back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But fifty years is a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hex got old. Then he got senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He completely forgot about\Nthe traps that he himself had set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better for you this way.\NYou know he won't expose you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dirty little secret\Nwill remain a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't tell anyone about the\Ndefects you built into the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it then.\NYou don't have to worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, money? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your price to keep from\Nleaking this thing to the press?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave the old guy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Call off the bounty hunters.\NThat's all we ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Ed would be unhappy if\Nshe lost her favorite chess partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And we wouldn't want that\Nto happen, now would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you playing {\i1}again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again, Ed's {\i1}still{\i0} playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... you've played\Nthe same game for a week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mm-hmm.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, newbie! You're in a good mood today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy there, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an easy-goin' dude, ain't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is, Antonio. Nice fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate! Checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me...
