Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Love... is to believe in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the heart\Nthat gives to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...\N{\i1}That's{\i0} what the story's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the heart\Nthat accepts everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}know{\i0} I'm not buying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitney, you loved me that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't trust\Nthe previews on this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.53,0:24:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A romantic love story\Nfor all you lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.13,0:24:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode:\N"My Funny Valentine."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.36,0:24:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's making it up.
